	<h1 class="title">国家图书馆在北京建了一座地铁图书馆</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37534/small/37534.JPG?1421809836" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">石玉</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-19 16:04:16 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7569/medium/7569.jpg?1436691553" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


